sub_title: ♜ I give professional guidance to become a better chess player | Professional Chess Trainer | Founder of DCA
summary:
My big passion in live is chess. I live my dream life, because my passion is also my work on a daily basis. I started as a successful chess player and in 2007 I made my first Grandmaster title. 

With almost 20 years experience as a chess teacher I teach teach top talents, but also enthusiastic amateur chess players. For foreign students I offer online chess lessons in English. Many of my pupils got international titles, impressive tournament victories or remarkable progress.

I am founder of the Delemarre Chess Academy (DCA). The DCA is a network organisation and collaborates with other chess trainers, local organisations and the national chess federation. It is our goal to help chess players, clubs and tournaments to achieve a higher level.

At the moment the DCA also collaborates with chess players in Belgium, Germany, India, Emirates, Hongkong and the US. 

______________________________________________________________________________
You want to know more about me, the DCA and how we can collaborate? 
Please contact me.
